List items (changes by default). Use --specs or --modules to list other items

Usage: spool list [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --no-color     Disable color output
      --specs        List specs instead of changes
      --changes      List changes explicitly (default)
      --help-all     Print the full CLI reference (equivalent to `spool help --all`)
      --modules      List modules instead of changes
      --sort <SORT>  Sort order [default: recent] [possible values: recent, name]
      --json         Output as JSON
  -h, --help         Print help
